[{"video_id": "tMgkt9jdjTU", "like_count": 1, "comment": "Swedish fella over here - I went to a party back in high school (2013) and met a friends friend while waiting for the bus and I remember this guy mentioned that he was cousin with yung lean. He proceeded to shove ginseng strip yt video in my face while on the bus clearly showing how proud he was of lean. The day after the party I remember checking out yung lean and I realized that this kid had one or two bangers with a couple million views on youtube and at the time I thought it was kinda aight but I never thought he would persist. That was my first encounter with lean, on a cold rainy dark October night in 2013. And holy fuck he grew on me over the next years. Like many of you say in the comments, he was so ahead of his time and I know some people even refer to him as the godfather of \"cloud rap\".  Its so crazy to see so many years later how his ginseng strip was blowing up on tik tok and all that. Im happy for the dude, seems so down to earth and great character. S A D B O Y S <3"}]
